Constructor Detail

Product

public Product(BoundName name,
               @Nullable
               Documentation help,
               GlobRelation filesAndParams,
               java.util.List<? extends Action> actions,
               boolean isIntermediate,
               @Nullable
               MobileFunction bake,
               java.nio.file.Path source)
Parameters:
name - a unique name that identifies this product. This is the name that will be used in with the build command, so $ bake build cake will build the product named "cake".
help - optional documentation.
filesAndParams - bundles the inputs, the set of files that need to be present when this product's actions are executed; with the outputs, the set of files that the product produces; with any parameters needed before this product is concrete enough to be included in a Recipe.
actions - the commands to execute to produce the outputs from the inputs.
isIntermediate - true if this product is required by other products but should not be explicitly built by the user.
bake - null or a mobile function that, at bake time, receives a function that builds each action, and can choose to run some and not others, and reinterpret results.
